      <h2>What We Actually See on Samsung Calls in Southern California</h2>
      <p>Samsung has been one of the top-selling appliance brands in Southern California for over a decade. We handle more Samsung calls than any other brand across our LA, OC, and Ventura routes. The failure patterns are predictable once you've done enough of them — and we have.</p>
      <p>The refrigerator ice maker freeze-out is our highest-volume Samsung call. The coastal environment along SoCal's coastline — from Malibu through Santa Monica, Newport Beach, Dana Point, and down to San Clemente — accelerates this failure. Homes near the Pacific see it in 2-3 years. Inland homes see it at 5-6 years. Same mechanism, different timeline. We explain the cause, not just the fix, and we install the duct cover kit that slows the recurrence.</p>
      <p>The Samsung washer OE error is the second-most-common call. In the majority of cases it's a clogged filter, not a pump failure. We clear it, show the homeowner where the filter is, and tell them quarterly. Most people have owned the machine for years without knowing the filter exists.</p>
      <p>On compressor calls: we check Samsung's 10-year inverter warranty before quoting any compressor job. Diagnostic fee is $89, credited toward the repair. Call your nearest branch.</p>
    </div>
